name: CUSTOM XBOX 360 CONTROLLERS & ACCESSORIES
blurb: Swagger Modz is ready to take our business to the NEXT LEVEL and we want you to be a part of our gaming legacy!

rewards.reward: Bragging rights and the opportunity to gain some karma for helping out some nerdy gamers.
A Swagger Modz "Swag Boy" sticker so you can let everyone know who made your custom controller!

A custom drawstring pouch for your controller or whatever you want to use it for. (Think Crown Royal bag, but no booze and way cooler) However, with the padded and super soft lining, carrying the controller in it may be the best idea. Plus you get the sticker and the karma.
A really comfy Swagger Modz T-shirt to wear to all of the watering holes and eateries you frequent. Plus we'll throw in the fuzzy controller pouch, the Swag Boy sticker & of course the karma.

A "Black Line" XBox 360 Controller. It's your basic black controller with a little more SWAG. It comes with your choice of colored sticks, buttons, triggers, trim, & coordinating LEDS. Plus we'll throw in the comfy shirt, fuzzy pouch, sticker, & karma.

A "Candy Shop" XBOX 360 controller. Custom painted controller in your choice of Candy Color Paint. Think of any car from "Pimp My Ride".... but without Xzibit. Matching LEDs and all black sticks, buttons, triggers and trim. Plus the comfy shirt, custom pouch and the bragging rights. BONUS: We'll put your gamertag or name or whatever short phrase you'd like ON THE CONTROLLER!

Custom hydro dipped 360 controller with your choice of design.  Plus the comfy shirt, custom pouch and the bragging rights. BONUS: We'll put your gamertag or name or whatever short phrase you'd like ON THE CONTROLLER!

A COORDINATING SET OF CONTROLLERS!! That's right, 2 controllers. It will be hydro dipped with your choice of design and the other will be a coordinating opposite. You'll also get 2 comfy shirts, 2 custom pouches, a couple of stickers and 2 tons of karma.

A custom LIMITED EDITION XBOX 360 CONTROLLER that everyone of your friends will envy. Customized throughout every detail. Only the backers who pledge $300 or more will receive this controller. Each controller will be numbered and WILL NEVER BE REPLICATED. And of course if you're shelling out the big bucks, we'll throw you a SWAG BAG full of fun stuff. Like the really comfy shirt, the super padded and fuzzy bag, the Swag Boy sticker and a whole truck load of karma. BONUS: Pick one (1) of the Black Line or Candy Shop controllers.

TWO (2) custom LIMITED EDITION XBOX 360 CONTROLLER that everyone of your friends will envy. Customized throughout every detail. Only the backers who pledge $300 or more will receive this controller. Each controller will be numbered and WILL NEVER BE REPLICATED. And of course if you're making it rain like Drake at a "cabaret", we'll throw you a SWAG BAG full of fun stuff. Like a couple really comfy shirts, the super padded and fuzzy bag (1 for each controller), Swag Boy stickers and a lifetime supply of karma.
